title: What's the name of that place you come from nan?
creator_credit: Rita Hinekauia Morrison and ACMI Digital Storytelling
brief_description: Rita comes from a mixed cultural background but her strongest connection is with the Maori side of her family. She shares her memories and family history in this digital story so that her Maori heritage can be preserved through future generations.
